cps.entities.models

Class ParkingCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • cps.entities.models.ParkingCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ParkingCell
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a parking cell as a data object that can be sent through the network and persisted in the database. A parking cell is the single unit of parking inside of a parking lot. One parking cell contains one car.
    See Also:
